51
00:03:06,219 --> 00:03:07,379
(Who are you?)

52
00:03:09,979 --> 00:03:11,159
(Sword Master.)

53
00:03:12,099 --> 00:03:13,259
(Your duty)

54
00:03:13,979 --> 00:03:17,139
(is to destroy the vessel
sealing the Night Deity)

55
00:03:17,340 --> 00:03:18,699
(and eliminate the Night Deity.)

56
00:03:20,099 --> 00:03:21,300
(Kill her.)

57
00:03:22,740 --> 00:03:24,539
(Only by killing her)

58
00:03:25,099 --> 00:03:27,979
(can we stop the Night Deity's reign
over the Three Realms.)

59
00:03:29,819 --> 00:03:31,099
(Ye Chenyuan.)

60
00:03:32,419 --> 00:03:34,280
(You're of the immortal sect,)

61
00:03:34,699 --> 00:03:36,419
(the Sword Master of the Three Realms.)

62
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,819
(You must protect the world)

63
00:03:39,139 --> 00:03:41,060
(from the Night Deity's reign.)

64
00:03:41,979 --> 00:03:43,340
(Kill her.)

65
00:03:45,300 --> 00:03:46,439
Those immortal cultivators

66
00:03:46,580 --> 00:03:48,620
still refuse to submit.

67
00:03:51,419 --> 00:03:52,500
Then keep torturing them

68
00:03:53,379 --> 00:03:55,060
until they beg for mercy.

69
00:03:55,979 --> 00:03:57,020
If we continue,

70
00:03:57,180 --> 00:03:58,300
they might die.

71
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,560
That's not your concern.

72
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,460
Just do what I say.

73
00:04:04,060 --> 00:04:04,599
Yes.

74
00:04:16,379 --> 00:04:17,920
If you had recovered,

75
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:20,139
staring at me like this

76
00:04:21,420 --> 00:04:23,019
would make me think you had evil plans.

77
00:04:44,060 --> 00:04:45,420
What are you...?

78
00:04:47,699 --> 00:04:48,920
Stop being so stern.

79
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:52,079
You could try smiling.

80
00:05:06,899 --> 00:05:07,699
I once said

81
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:10,540
the same words to you.

82
00:05:12,579 --> 00:05:13,399
Now,

83
00:05:14,379 --> 00:05:15,660
you're the one telling me this.

84
00:05:18,379 --> 00:05:20,300
Do you remember why I said these

85
00:05:21,740 --> 00:05:22,560
to you?

86
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:28,459
I only remember the words

87
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,800
and saw you are upset,

88
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,939
so I repeat them to you.

89
00:05:37,540 --> 00:05:38,480
I've been occupied,

90
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:39,920
feeling troubled.

91
00:05:40,860 --> 00:05:41,819
But I feel better

92
00:05:42,540 --> 00:05:43,339
seeing you.

93
00:05:58,459 --> 00:05:59,259
Ye Chenyuan.

94
00:06:01,620 --> 00:06:02,980
Do you know what you're doing?

95
00:06:06,100 --> 00:06:07,220
Combing your hair.

96
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,399
Do you know?

97
00:06:10,819 --> 00:06:12,459
When a man combs a woman's hair,

98
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:15,779
it means he'll marry her,

99
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:18,620
to stay together

100
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:19,860
until their death.

101
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:25,180
I don't.

102
00:06:26,660 --> 00:06:27,860
But I can ask.

103
00:06:33,019 --> 00:06:34,139
What's there to ask?

104
00:06:36,019 --> 00:06:37,220
Since you've combed my hair,

105
00:06:37,860 --> 00:06:39,220
you are mine now.

106
00:06:42,420 --> 00:06:43,620
In that case,

107
00:06:44,459 --> 00:06:46,000
you must grant me a wish.

108
00:06:48,699 --> 00:06:49,779
