129
00:09:07,899 --> 00:09:08,580
The Lord said

130
00:09:08,820 --> 00:09:10,580
no one allowed to go in.

131
00:09:13,620 --> 00:09:14,659
It's the Lord's token.

132
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:16,419
Please forgive our ignorance.

133
00:09:18,379 --> 00:09:19,460
You're not needed here.

134
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:21,100
Go rest.

135
00:09:21,820 --> 00:09:23,259
I'll get someone else later.

136
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:24,139
Yes.

137
00:09:40,340 --> 00:09:41,539
Bai Xiaoying's lackey.

138
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:42,620
Why are you here?

139
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:43,340
Get lost!

140
00:09:43,820 --> 00:09:45,860
He must have found
new ways to torture us.

141
00:09:46,379 --> 00:09:47,620
Go back and tell Bai Xiaoying

142
00:09:47,940 --> 00:09:48,659
we're not afraid.

143
00:09:49,899 --> 00:09:50,659
Time's running out.

144
00:09:51,379 --> 00:09:52,139
Leave now.

145
00:09:55,419 --> 00:09:56,340
You don't kill us,

146
00:09:57,379 --> 00:09:58,179
but let us go?

147
00:10:01,379 --> 00:10:02,659
You serve Bai Xiaoying.

148
00:10:03,340 --> 00:10:04,460
Why let us escape?

149
00:10:06,139 --> 00:10:07,500
Just kill us.

150
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:08,220
Exactly.

151
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:10,940
They've definitely set a trap,

152
00:10:11,139 --> 00:10:12,620
waiting for us to fall into it.

153
00:10:13,139 --> 00:10:14,139
We won't take the bait.

154
00:10:14,419 --> 00:10:15,940
Don't trust him.

155
00:10:17,820 --> 00:10:18,980
I don't know who I am.

156
00:10:20,220 --> 00:10:20,940
I'm releasing you

157
00:10:21,779 --> 00:10:22,899
just because I want to.

158
00:10:23,659 --> 00:10:24,419
Stay or leave,

159
00:10:25,179 --> 00:10:26,100
it's up to you.

160
00:10:32,899 --> 00:10:33,419
Leave.

161
00:10:34,259 --> 00:10:35,019
No matter what,

162
00:10:35,340 --> 00:10:36,139
give it a try.

163
00:10:36,419 --> 00:10:36,899
Exactly.

164
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:38,220
Immortal Xiyuan is right.

165
00:10:38,460 --> 00:10:39,539
We have to give it a try.

166
00:10:41,139 --> 00:10:41,580
Let's go.

167
00:10:42,944 --> 00:10:43,520
Let's go.

168
00:10:49,259 --> 00:10:50,059
Ye Chenyuan.

169
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:53,500
Maybe only you

170
00:10:54,179 --> 00:10:55,179
can save Bai Xiaoying.

171
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,100
At midnight,

172
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:23,639
you're not asleep.

173
00:11:23,980 --> 00:11:24,740
What did you do?

174
00:11:26,059 --> 00:11:26,679
I...

175
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:28,559
I...

176
00:11:33,620 --> 00:11:35,379
Why would you defy me?

177
00:11:38,379 --> 00:11:39,580
You think I've done wrong too?

178
00:11:41,059 --> 00:11:43,340
Do you know how those people treated us?

179
00:11:44,779 --> 00:11:46,259
We've suffered much.

180
00:11:47,639 --> 00:11:49,039
It's all their fault.

181
00:11:54,860 --> 00:11:55,580
Fine.

182
00:11:57,179 --> 00:11:59,019
I've been too lenient with you.

183
00:12:00,019 --> 00:12:01,620
Since you let them go,

184
00:12:02,639 --> 00:12:03,559
then you shall

185
00:12:04,399 --> 00:12:05,759
atone for their sins.

186
00:12:28,460 --> 00:12:29,379
You should

187
00:12:29,980 --> 00:12:31,179
be familiar with this place.

188
00:12:33,620 --> 00:12:34,740
But this time,

189
00:12:35,220 --> 00:12:36,340
it'll be different.

190
00:12:37,620 --> 00:12:38,379
What comes next

191
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:41,259
is my grand gift for you.

192
00:12:57,620 --> 00:12:59,620
This herbal bath was special for you.

193
00:13:01,940 --> 00:13:03,620
You defied me.

194
00:13:04,220 --> 00:13:05,620
I bet this small pain

195
00:13:06,259 --> 00:13:07,500
would be nothing to you.

196
00:13:12,059 --> 00:13:12,860
Does doing this

197
00:13:14,139 --> 00:13:15,059
bring you joy?

198
00:13:20,740 --> 00:13:21,899
Of course.

199
00:13:23,299 --> 00:13:24,580
Why not?

200
00:13:26,019 --> 00:13:27,419
Everything

201
00:13:28,220 --> 00:13:29,779
I've done

202
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:31,820
is all for you.

203
00:13:32,820 --> 00:13:34,580
I've done so much for you,

204
00:13:35,700 --> 00:13:37,460
just to be with you,

205
00:13:38,580 --> 00:13:40,179
yet you betrayed me!

206
00:13:43,179 --> 00:13:44,100
Listen.

207
00:13:44,980 --> 00:13:46,379
You are mine.

208
00:13:47,700 --> 00:13:49,100
From now on,

209
00:13:50,379 --> 00:13:51,820
don't even think of defying me.

210
00:13:54,220 --> 00:13:55,500
First bow to heaven and earth!

211
00:13:56,820 --> 00:13:58,179
Second bow to the parents!

212
00:13:58,940 --> 00:14:00,259
The couple bows to each other!

213
00:14:01,820 --> 00:14:02,620
Then why

214
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:06,220
have I already married?

215
00:14:09,419 --> 00:14:11,539
I-I saw

216
00:14:12,100 --> 00:14:13,259
the cabin in Snowfall Valley.

217
00:14:16,059 --> 00:14:17,419
I was performing wedding rites.

218
00:14:19,860 --> 00:14:20,419
Yes.

219
00:14:22,139 --> 00:14:23,100
We married.

220
00:14:24,139 --> 00:14:25,019
You remember now?

221
00:14:29,539 --> 00:14:30,220
Pity

222
00:14:33,019 --> 00:14:34,820
we didn't complete the rites.

223
00:14:38,820 --> 00:14:39,860
But that's fine.

224
00:14:40,620 --> 00:14:43,019
After we properly hold the wedding,

225
00:14:43,620 --> 00:14:44,419
from then on,

226
00:14:45,379 --> 00:14:47,299
we'll be a legitimate couple.

227
00:15:33,059 --> 00:15:33,700
Look at me.

228
00:16:11,899 --> 00:16:13,019
(Yunya was right.)

229
00:16:14,139 --> 00:16:15,980
(My body won't last long.)

230
00:16:17,460 --> 00:16:20,139
(But Ye Chenyuan has only retrieved
some of his souls and spirits.)

231
00:16:21,460 --> 00:16:22,620
(I can't wait any longer.)

232
00:16:38,980 --> 00:16:39,980
I've already arranged it.

233
00:16:40,700 --> 00:16:41,580
In ten days,

234
00:16:41,940 --> 00:16:43,139
we'll hold the wedding.

235
00:16:45,419 --> 00:16:46,500
I didn't agree.

236
00:16:49,940 --> 00:16:51,340
I'm here to inform you,

237
00:16:52,139 --> 00:16:53,659
not to seek your approval.

238
00:16:55,356 --> 00:16:56,032
(Wedding Invitation)

239
00:17:14,940 --> 00:17:16,099
Here, this is yours.

240
00:17:20,099 --> 00:17:20,900
Take it slow.

241
00:17:24,339 --> 00:17:25,500
Chief, everything is ready.

242
00:17:25,980 --> 00:17:27,380
Good. Go ahead.

243
00:17:29,220 --> 00:17:30,660
Sorry for bothering you.

244
00:17:31,420 --> 00:17:31,980
By the way,

245
00:17:32,299 --> 00:17:33,539
I've brought you the antidote.

246
00:17:39,059 --> 00:17:41,539
Ye Chenyuan stole it from Bai Xiaoying.

247
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:50,240
Thank you.

248
00:17:51,259 --> 00:17:52,500
We should be thanking you.

249
00:17:52,980 --> 00:17:54,259
If you hadn't taken us in,

250
00:17:54,619 --> 00:17:56,660
we'd have been captured
by Bai Xiaoying long ago.

251
00:17:59,299 --> 00:18:00,619
I think it's because

252
00:18:01,059 --> 00:18:04,220
Bai Xiaoying and Ye Chenyuan
will hold the wedding in ten days.

253
00:18:05,220 --> 00:18:06,619
They probably

254
00:18:07,700 --> 00:18:09,059
don't have time

255
00:18:09,579 --> 00:18:10,779
for you now.

256
00:18:11,980 --> 00:18:12,900
So,

257
00:18:13,259 --> 00:18:14,259
in ten days,

258
00:18:16,420 --> 00:18:18,619
it will be our best chance
to rescue the Immortal Lord.

259
00:18:33,059 --> 00:18:33,900
Hurry up.

260
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:35,799
The Lord's wedding is in ten days.

261
00:18:36,019 --> 00:18:37,019
Be careful of everything.

262
00:18:37,140 --> 00:18:37,960
Be quick.

263
00:18:43,660 --> 00:18:44,380
Rest assured.

264
00:18:45,140 --> 00:18:46,619
Weakening Powder makes you weak,

265
00:18:47,180 --> 00:18:48,859
but won't physically harm you.

266
00:18:50,299 --> 00:18:51,579
After our wedding,

267
00:18:52,140 --> 00:18:53,140
you'll get the antidote.

268
00:18:54,339 --> 00:18:55,380
Stop this.

269
00:18:56,019 --> 00:18:57,019
It's still not too late.

270
00:19:01,819 --> 00:19:03,140
Never.

271
00:19:09,980 --> 00:19:10,900
Take a rest here.

272
00:19:11,539 --> 00:19:12,861
I'll check on our wedding attire.

273
00:19:41,359 --> 00:19:42,559
This revised one looks better.

274
00:19:43,460 --> 00:19:44,380
Come try it.

275
00:19:48,099 --> 00:19:48,700
Ye Chenyuan!

276
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:55,920
Find him.

277
00:19:57,019 --> 00:19:58,259
He can't have gone far.

278
00:19:58,859 --> 00:20:00,700
Search every corner of the Three Realms

279
00:20:01,099 --> 00:20:02,299
to bring him back to me.

280
00:20:02,420 --> 00:20:03,140
- Understood.
- Understood.

281
00:20:19,380 --> 00:20:20,160
Ye Chenyuan.

282
00:20:25,319 --> 00:20:25,960
Why?

283
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:28,839
I drugged you,

284
00:20:29,079 --> 00:20:29,960
and you can't escape.

285
00:20:30,359 --> 00:20:31,759
Why still try to escape?

286
00:20:34,279 --> 00:20:35,460
Do you hate me that much?

287
00:20:36,839 --> 00:20:38,279
